26
00:01:10,340 --> 00:01:11,550
[You want to decline it?]

27
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:13,610
Yun Shu,

28
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,950
even experienced illustrators

29
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,070
even eager for this chance.

30
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:19,310
You are really lucky to have
this opportunity as a newbie.

31
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:20,840
So give it careful thought.

32
00:01:20,930 --> 00:01:21,810
Mei,

33
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:23,260
I've made up my mind.

34
00:01:25,030 --> 00:01:27,050
Do you know what you are giving up?

35
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,390
Of course, if you don't go
to Kobayashi Studio,

36
