54
00:02:03,940 --> 00:02:04,820
Go ahead.

55
00:02:08,020 --> 00:02:08,900
Yun Shu.

56
00:02:10,830 --> 00:02:12,670
If you need my help
with your family affairs,

57
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,640
