59
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,680
in order to talk with you alone.

60
00:02:24,770 --> 00:02:26,170
Is it about Han Rong?

61
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:28,340
Yes.

62
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:30,570
Lu Yu doesn't want me to
get involved.

63
00:02:30,790 --> 00:02:31,990
He will figure it out.

64
00:02:32,130 --> 00:02:33,850
I won't come today

65
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:35,530
if he can work it out.

66
