Trust should be mutual.

84
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:39,420
It can't be forced.

85
00:03:39,530 --> 00:03:41,170
What if I insist for you to continue?

86
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,080
You must know about what happened

87
00:03:47,459 --> 00:03:48,370
between Lu Yu and me.

88
00:03:48,459 --> 00:03:49,500
If you can continue to be

89
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,610
our legal advisor,

90
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:53,209
maybe I can

91
