cut him some slack.

92
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:55,500
Mr Han,

93
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:57,770
are you threatening me?

94
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,300
According to Article 226

95
00:03:59,390 --> 00:04:00,820
of the Chinese Criminal Law,

96
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,020
one can be penalized

97
00:04:03,110 --> 00:04:04,590
for forcing others to provide services

98
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,530
or to receive services

99
00:04:06,780 --> 00:04:08,510
by threatening.

100
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,960
It's not a threat.

101
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,960
It's a compromise.

102
00:04:14,410 --> 00:04:15,470
This USD stick contains

103
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,890
the footage of what happened that day.

104
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,590
It clearly shows Lu Yu and his action.

105
00:04:21,710 --> 00:04:24,000
It also contains
the injury assessment done by

106
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:26,130
a professional institution.

107
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:28,110
Lu Yu will

108
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,820
lose in this case.

109
00:04:30,090 --> 00:04:31,690
Now you're underestimating me.

110
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,370
I never look down on women,

111
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:37,600
let alone you.

112
00:04:37,690 --> 00:04:39,380
I don't know the
entertainment industry well.

113
00:04:39,530 --> 00:04:40,930
But I know people

114
00:04:41,010 --> 00:04:44,300
will gossip in this circle.

115
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,970
The project has gotten the green light.

116
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:56,550
I'll go abroad

117
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,950
very soon.

118
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,930
Congratulations.

119
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:00,850
Also,

120
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,380
have a safe trip.

121
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,640
You've made up your mind?

122
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:09,180
Will you take grandpa
to get treatment abroad?

123
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,460
Grandpa is not in a good shape.

124
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:13,070
So I'm not sure

125
00:05:13,150 --> 00:05:14,870
whether he can bear the

126
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,270
long journey.

127
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:21,500
Are you just caring about grandpa?

128
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:25,840
What do you mean?

129
00:05:26,820 --> 00:05:28,960
I think you can't leave Yun Shu behind

130
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:30,840
and you don't want to part with her.

131
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,550
You think too much.

132
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:41,130
Though we're not in love,

133
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:43,100
you have to admit that

134
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:45,420
we're alike.

135
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:48,310
I can understand your hesitation.

136
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:50,030
But this chance

137
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:52,620
is grandpa's last hope.

138
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,170
I won't give up my grandpa.

139
