This is my first time reading
such a thesis.

140
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:31,300
Is it not good enough?

141
00:06:32,690 --> 00:06:34,280
It must be because you didn't do well,

142
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,630
so you stapled the four corners to

143
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,860
prevent me from reading it.

144
00:06:40,609 --> 00:06:42,229
I... I'll open it.

145
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,760
Yun Shu,

146
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,410
what's wrong?

147
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,950
Why are you uneasy?

148
00:07:02,590 --> 00:07:03,700
I've been thinking about

149
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:06,150
grandpa recently.

150
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:07,840
So,

151
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,570
I can't calm down.

152
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:14,690
Grandpa will be okay.

153
00:07:15,050 --> 00:07:16,200
Rest assured.

154
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,690
I still think that

155
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:26,710
we should send grandpa overseas.

156
00:07:27,610 --> 00:07:29,460
Maybe it's a slim hope,

157
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:31,440
but we shouldn't give it up.

158
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,200
You're going to have your final defense.

159
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:43,970
So forget about that first.

160
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,860
Be ready for your final defense.

161
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,610
As for grandpa's illness,

162
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:51,470
