167
00:08:24,050 --> 00:08:25,110
You're preoccupied.

168
00:08:25,330 --> 00:08:26,220
Nothing special.

169
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,400
Some documents.

170
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,170
