180
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:49,310
It is temporarily suspended.

181
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,330
Really?

182
00:08:51,810 --> 00:08:52,510
What's going on?

183
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,740
Why are you so suspicious?

184
00:08:56,620 --> 00:08:57,500
What is it?

185
00:08:58,040 --> 00:09:00,220
