190
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,880
Nothing.

191
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,870
Okay, I got it.

192
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:52,100
Mr Zhang.

193
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,820
I knew it.

194
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:56,210
