00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,030
You're late, Yun Lan.

236
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,160
Come on.

237
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:51,080
Sit over here.

238
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:55,580
Yun Lan.

239
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,990
What's going on?

240
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,150
Yun Lan

241
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,960
is my attorney.

242
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:05,110
Okay. Since we're all here,
let's get it started.

243
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,530
What on earth is going on?

244
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:08,630
Why are you this scum's attorney?

245
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,320
Yun Lan.

246
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,810
Add libel to his list of offence.

247
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,890
Shut up.

248
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:14,960
Explain it.

249
00:12:15,090 --> 00:12:16,520
Let's get down to business.

250
00:12:16,850 --> 00:12:17,960
We can talk later.

251
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,300
No., tell me now.

252
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,830
Yun Lan is our company's legal advisor.

253
00:12:22,930 --> 00:12:24,380
So there's nothing wrong with her

254
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:26,190
being my attorney.

255
00:12:29,730 --> 00:12:30,750
Hold on.

256
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,360
Don't be so impulsive.

257
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,540
I'm not impulsive.

258
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:37,990
I just want to ask you one question.

259
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,440
Are you sure about taking this case?

260
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:40,410
Yes.

261
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:42,940
I'm taking this case because...

262
00:12:43,020 --> 00:12:43,970
The company?

263
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:44,940
For money?

264
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,470
For your career and ambition?

265
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,420
That's what you think of me?

266
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,780
We're in a relationship.

267
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,230
But you never sacrificed anything for me.

268
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,100
No even the slightest bit
of compromise.

269
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,000
Yun Lan.

270
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,730
Sometimes, I really wonder
if you care about me at all.

271
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:06,130
Can we stop talking about this here?

272
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:07,360
Am I wrong?

273
00:13:07,470 --> 00:13:08,410
Do you love me?

274
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,860
If you love me, just tell me right now.

275
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:12,750
Can you stop being childish?

276
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,590
-Come on.
-I'm being childish?

277
00:13:15,370 --> 00:13:16,820
You know that I was slandered,

278
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:17,900
but you're on his side.

279
00:13:17,980 --> 00:13:19,590
Is that supposed to be maturity?

280
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:20,620
Lu Yu.

281
00:13:21,590 --> 00:13:23,230
I can explain it.

282
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:25,220
-It's not what you think.
-Save it, Yun Lan.

283
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:27,220
We're over.

284
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:32,200
