00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:27,810
Yun Shu is so sweet.

574
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:42,320
Lin Nuo.

575
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:43,580
Lin Nuo.

576
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:47,100
Lin Nuo.

577
00:26:47,490 --> 00:26:48,730
Come on.

578
00:26:48,910 --> 00:26:50,070
You're avoiding me as if I were a virus.

579
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,530
Are you really so sick of me?

580
00:26:52,530 --> 00:26:53,410
Go home.

581
00:26:53,770 --> 00:26:55,070
Please leave me alone.

582
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:58,310
Gu Xiao and I aren't together.

583
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:00,510
Have a look.

584
00:27:01,650 --> 00:27:03,010
I deleted his WeChat.

585
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:03,980
Yi Yi.

586
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:06,280
It's over between us.

587
00:27:06,930 --> 00:27:08,680
But we can start over.

588
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:10,500
We can start from being friends.

589
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,900
Lin Nuo, I've changed.

590
00:27:12,990 --> 00:27:14,310
If you still can't believe me,

591
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:15,750
we can go to get a marriage certificate.

592
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,310
I brought my household register.

593
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:22,160
Lin Nuo,

594
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:24,430
I know I treated you badly.

595
00:27:24,550 --> 00:27:26,490
I know you've liked me since before.

596
00:27:26,700 --> 00:27:28,750
I thought you would never leave me.

597
00:27:28,980 --> 00:27:31,630
So I took advantage
of your affection towards me.

598
00:27:31,730 --> 00:27:33,700
I understand why you're sick of me now.

599
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:34,670
But,

600
00:27:34,810 --> 00:27:36,220
I need to tell you

601
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:38,010
or I'll regret it.

602
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,000
Yi Yi.

603
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:41,380
It's too late.

604
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,350
I'm leaving for Africa next month.

605
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:45,030
Next month?

606
00:27:45,510 --> 00:27:46,230
Yes.

607
00:27:46,320 --> 00:27:47,750
You're going there for a trip?

608
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,490
-I can...
-No.

609
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,840
I'm going there to work.

610
00:27:51,170 --> 00:27:52,380
Medical support.

611
00:27:53,410 --> 00:27:54,460
For how long?

612
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:56,020
It doesn't matter.

613
00:27:57,170 --> 00:27:58,310
I will go

614
00:27:58,390 --> 00:27:59,570
with Xia Lin.

615
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:04,320
Yi Yi.

616
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:06,190
I'm not sick of you

617
00:28:06,390 --> 00:28:08,130
because I've let go of

618
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:10,390
my feelings for you.

619
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:13,330
You'll find the one

620
00:28:13,630 --> 00:28:15,060
who loves you

621
00:28:15,610 --> 00:28:17,180
sooner or later.

622
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:18,900
I think

623
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:21,070
you won't remember me at that time.

624
00:29:10,620 --> 00:29:11,680
Mr Zhang.

625
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,330
What's going on?

626
00:29:14,420 --> 00:29:15,670
Stop here.

627
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:23,020
I'm afraid that I won't

628
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:24,660
go through security

629
00:29:24,750 --> 00:29:26,740
and board the plane

630
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:28,450
because you're there.

631
00:29:30,570 --> 00:29:31,750
Just stop here.

632
00:29:39,230 --> 00:29:40,110
Okay.

633
00:29:40,430 --> 00:29:42,540
Check whether everything is ready.

634
00:29:42,630 --> 00:29:44,300
Remember the passport.

635
00:29:44,690 --> 00:29:45,520
It's alright.

636
00:29:45,610 --> 00:29:46,830
I have everything.

637
00:29:56,670 --> 00:30:01,970
♫ Turning off the lights
in search of its trace ♫

638
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,560
Alright.

639
00:30:01,520 --> 00:30:03,560
Go or you will miss the plane.

640
00:30:02,770 --> 00:30:08,050
♫ I walk steadily
on the path beneath my feet ♫

641
00:30:06,730 --> 00:30:08,690
I'll be back to send you and grandpa off

642
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:14,380
♫ I hear someone asking,
are you still here? ♫

643
00:30:08,780 --> 00:30:10,860
in a week.

644
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:13,730
That's a deal.

645
00:30:14,470 --> 00:30:16,420
Go now or you'll be late.

646
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:20,230
♫ The kind person replies,
I've always been here ♫

647
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:24,300
♫ This love cuts through the crowd
in search of me ♫

648
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:26,380
♫ It isn't easy ♫

649
00:30:26,870 --> 00:30:30,140
♫ I only wish to cherish it with you ♫

650
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:32,540
♫ Each and every moment ♫

651
00:30:33,100 --> 00:30:38,310
♫ If I missed out, I will meet you again
in another lifetime ♫

652
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:44,980
♫ I recognise your eyes,
a secret that belongs to me ♫

653
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:48,040
Lin Nuo, I won't fall in love with others.

654
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:50,170
I will only wait for you.

655
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:51,160
Yi Yi.

656
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,680
Let it go.

657
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:55,020
We have to move on.

658
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:58,710
Lin Nuo.

659
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,990
I know I was wrong.

660
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,860
I know I treated you badly.

661
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:05,000
I don't know why I was so mean to you.

662
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:07,830
I feel really regretful now.

663
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,780
Can you give me one more chance?

664
00:31:09,860 --> 00:31:10,830
What do you think?

665
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:13,480
Someone who loved me so much before

666
00:31:13,700 --> 00:31:15,630
can't possibly feel nothing now.

667
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:19,390
I didn't believe the words

668
00:31:19,490 --> 00:31:20,470
that said

669
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:22,930
we can meet the right one at right time.

670
00:31:23,800 --> 00:31:26,100
I believed love should come naturally.

671
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,650
It's not about the right and wrong.

672
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:30,940
But after we experienced so much,

673
00:31:31,100 --> 00:31:32,630
I began to believe that

674
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,840
what they said is true.

675
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,320
If the timing is wrong,

676
00:31:36,410 --> 00:31:37,510
even if we're in love,

677
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:39,800
we'll miss each other.

678
00:31:42,950 --> 00:31:44,730
So I missed out on you.

679
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:48,080
No.

680
00:31:50,470 --> 00:31:52,050
We can still be friends.

681
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:55,890
Best friends forever.

682
00:32:23,810 --> 00:32:24,689
Take care.
